Use weather api https://www.weatherapi.com/docs/ to create following application

Once we click on any location then we will land on its detail page with current weather information
At location detail page we need to have mutiple buttons
Current weather
Forecast
History
Time Zone
Sports
Astronomy
Weather Alerts
Air Quality
All the buttons have its own meaning, so do needful
After basic cURL, do same task with Guzzle library

